btcxInrateAvg(bytes32,uint256,bool).details: Calculates an average interest rate between after and before mint/redeem

params.btcAmount: Value of the operation from which calculates the inrate [using reservePrecision]
params.bucket: Name of the bucket involved in the operation
params.onMinting: Value that represents if the calculation is based on mint or on redeem

calcCommissionValue(uint256).details: calculates the Commission rate from the passed RBTC amount for mint/redeem operations

params.rbtcAmount: Total value from which apply the Commission rate [using reservePrecision]

calcDocRedInterestValues(uint256,uint256.details: Extract the inrate from the passed RBTC value for the Doc Redeem operation

params.docAmount: Doc amount of the redemption [using mocPrecision]
params.rbtcAmount: Total value from which extract the interest rate [using reservePrecision]

calcFinalRedeemInterestValue(bytes32,uin.details: This function calculates the interest to return to the user in a BPRox redemption. It uses a mechanism to counteract the effect of free docs redemption. It will be replaced with FreeDoC redemption interests in the future

params.rbtcToRedeem: Total value from which calculate interest [using reservePrecision]

calcFinalRedeemInterestValue(bytes32,uin.return: RBTC to recover in concept of interests [using reservePrecision]
